Package com.example.demo1

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Filter<E>
    Interface containing the abstract method for filter implementation.
    Stats<T>
    Interface containing the abstract method for math stats implementation
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller1
    Controller responsible for REST requests
    Data<T>
    Generic class that contains data referred to T class objects and utils.
    FieldParam
    This class contains other info for the filter method
    FieldParamAll
    This class will contain parameters used to entually filter the data set and stats
    FilterUtils<T>
    This class contains the methods for filtering and selecting objects from a data set of T class objects.
    MathUtils<T>
    Class containing all the methods used for math and word stats.
    MetaData
    Class containing attributes of metadata parsed by the csv.
    MetaSet
    Class containing all the RadioStation parsed metadata.
    ParseUtils
    This class contains all the methods for downloading the csv, converting JSONObjects, the parsing of data from the csv file to the RadioStation class and more.
    ProgettoOopApplication
    Spring boot application class containing the main class.
    ProgettoOopApplicationTests  
    RadioSet  
    RadioStation
    Class containing attributes of a single radio station parsed by the csv.
    SystemConfig
    Configuration class that defines the beans instantiated by Spring framework
    Utils<T>
    This class contains miscellaneous utilities such as: filter, stats, and parsing.
